# Bitcoin Tools & Scripts

A collection of Bitcoin‑related utilities, Termux‑compatible build scripts, and workflow tools designed for Android environments.  
This repository includes:

- Build scripts for Bitcoin Core (Termux‑optimized)
- Raw transaction construction helpers
- UTXO analysis tools
- Automation utilities for Android/Termux
- GitHub‑ready release structure

---

## 🚀 Features

### ✔ Termux‑Optimized Build Scripts
- Compile Bitcoin Core v27.0+ on Android 16
- Fully static builds with wallet disabled
- Automatic dependency checks

### ✔ Transaction & UTXO Tools
- Raw transaction templates
- Hex assembly helpers
- Fee estimation utilities
- Broadcast helpers using `curl`

### ✔ Blockchain Analysis
- TSV/CSV parsing for Blockchair datasets
- UTXO fan‑out tracing
- Block template inspection

---

